<text id="02-output-contract" title="Django Testing with pytest — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="900" depth="essential">
  <summary>Output schema for the subagent applying django-testing. Encodes required boolean checks against the artefact under review.</summary>

  <section title="Schema (JSON Schema fragment)">
    <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "$schema": "https://json-schema.org/draft/2020-12/schema",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ['pytest_config_present', 'django_db_marker_present', 'format_json_used', 'force_authenticate_used', 'orm_mocking_count==0'],
  "properties": {
    "pytest_config_present": { "type": "boolean" },
    "django_db_marker_present": { "type": "boolean" },
    "format_json_used": { "type": "boolean" },
    "force_authenticate_used": { "type": "boolean" },
    "orm_mocking_count==0": { "type": "boolean" }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false
}
]]></code>
  </section>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>pytest_config_present</item>
      <item>django_db_marker_present</item>
      <item>format_json_used</item>
      <item>force_authenticate_used</item>
      <item>orm_mocking_count==0</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Valid example">
    <example type="good">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "pytest_config_present": true,
  "django_db_marker_present": true,
  "format_json_used": true,
  "force_authenticate_used": true,
  "orm_mocking_count==0": true
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates green; methodology applied.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Invalid example">
    <example type="bad">
      <code lang="json"><![CDATA[
{
  "pytest_config_present": false,
  "django_db_marker_present": false,
  "format_json_used": false,
  "force_authenticate_used": false,
  "orm_mocking_count==0": false
}
]]></code>
      <note>All gates red; methodology not applied — fix the violations before claiming completion.</note>
    </example>
  </section>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>Every required field is present and boolean true.</item>
      <item>Artefact references the rule id from 01-core-rules.xml (e.g., r1-pyproject-pytest-config).</item>
      <item>No extra properties outside the schema.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
